36 "§ 88B-15. Practice outside cosmetic art shops.
37 (a) Any individual licensed or certified under this Chapter may visit the residences of
38 individuals who are sick or disabled and confined to their places of residence in order to attend
39 to their cosmetic needs. A licensed or certified individual may also visit hospitals, nursing homes,
40 rest homes, retirement homes, mental institutions, correctional facilities, funeral homes, and
41 similar institutions to attend to the cosmetic needs of those in these institutions.
42 (b) An individual licensed or certified under this Chapter may practice in a licensed
43 barbershop as permitted by G.S. 86A-14.G.S. 86B-32.
