43 (2) Commissioned medical or surgical officers of the United States Army or other
44 components of the Armed Forces of the United States, and those working
45 under their supervision.
46 (3) Registered nurses and licensed practical nurses and those working under their
47 supervision.
48 (4) Licensed embalmers and funeral directors and those working under their
49 supervision.
